00:35:40.919 --> 00:35:46.840
to work on your desktop, here's the version we're supporting and here's a kind of get you started

00:35:46.840 --> 00:35:54.520
set. And, you know, we get that from RStudio Package Manager. But we're then kind of saying,

00:35:54.520 --> 00:36:00.280
look, your desktop is just a sandbox. You know, try stuff out. If it works, great. If it doesn't

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:05.639
work, whatever. And if you get into a complete mess, then just, you know, blow it all away and

00:36:05.639 --> 00:36:14.600
start again. We are tiptoeing into using our env package, or at least I'm trying to kind of persuade

