didn't work. Then it takes you a second to think, man, what else could it be, right? It could even

00:50:05.719 --> 00:50:10.840
be a flat tire, right? What are the reasons my tire went flat? And what are the reasons why my

00:50:11.639 --> 00:50:17.560
tire went flat? And I look at the tube, and this is the reason why the tube went flat. It's broken,

